---
import PlusIcon from '@/components/icons/PlusIcon.astro';
---

<div class="mt-10 mb-64">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- IT Consulting Service -->
        <article class="group flex flex-col border border-primary-turquoise/30  p-4 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-black to-primary-turquoise/10  rounded-xl">
            <header class="text-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-turquoise transition-colors duration-300">
                    IT Consulting
                </h3>
            </header>
            
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    We offer IT consulting services focused on identifying opportunities for technological improvement, optimizing infrastructure, and aligning digital solutions with your business's strategic objectives.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    Strategic diagnosis, roadmap definition, and creation of models that drive data-driven decisions and efficiencies.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Modern Web Development Service -->
        <article class="group flex flex-col border border-primary-turquoise/30 p-4 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-black to-primary-turquoise/10  rounded-xl">
            <header class="text-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-turquoise transition-colors duration-300">
                    Modern Web Development
                </h3>
            </header>
            
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    Combining best practices in responsive design, optimized speed, and cutting-edge technologies like React, Astro, and Tailwind CSS. We create personalized, scalable, and user-centric digital experiences.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    Robust digital interfaces tailored to your business model, optimized to scale and connect with your users more effectively.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- AI-Powered Automation Service -->
        <article class="group flex flex-col border border-primary-turquoise/30 p-4 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-black to-primary-turquoise/10 md:col-span-2 xl:col-span-1 rounded-xl">
            <header class="text-center mb-4 sm:mb-6"> 
                <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-turquoise transition-colors duration-300">
                    AI-Powered Automation
                </h3>
            </header>
            
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    We boost operational efficiency through advanced automation powered by artificial intelligence. We design and implement solutions that optimize workflows, integrate chatbots, analyze data in real time, and reduce repetitive tasks.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-neutral-400 text-pretty leading-relaxed group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
                    We design intelligent flows, chatbots and systems that automate repetitive tasks, improve customer response and reduce operating costs.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</div>
